<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENCP70A7216024" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Air Intake Switch Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENCP70A7216020">HVAC Control Unit Removal and Installation:Manual Type</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Check air intake switch for terminal-to-terminal continuity. If check result is not as specified, replace HVAC control unit.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
To perform measurement with air intake selector in “REC” position, use diode range of circuit tester.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
